@DATABASE "Yabba Dabba Dooo"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - Y - Yabba Dabba Dooo"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - Y
                   ====================================

                             Yabba Dabba Dooo
                             ================



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(43612,0)"}          43612,0
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(37003,22)"}          37003,x (x= 1-255)

                         Although the "Lives = x" can go up to 255, I
                         wouldn't put it to more than 22 as it will
                         fill the screen with lives (I's)..

                         Rastan.
@endnode
